product_title: Invicta Men's 8926OB Pro Diver Stainless Steel Automatic Watch with Link Bracelet
review_headline: Worth the money, be careful with the glass.
review_body:
Alrighty, after seeking out the ultimate low-profile, ultra water resistant, mechanical watch with a rotating bezel and date for less than $100, I settled on this.

It looks much like the famous Rolex Submariner, and performs similarly.

However, after about a year of use now, the paint on the bezel is chipping, and after a decent smack on the hood of a car the crystal has cracked and all but shattered.

It keeps time fairly well, gaining about 15 seconds per day, without taking it to a healer for fine tuning.

product_title: Invicta Men's 8928OB Pro Diver Gold Stainless Steel Two-Tone Automatic Watch
review_body:
This watch is a very beautiful time piece. This also could be an alternative choice to a Rolex submariner. It also has the same features as a Rolex submariner but it's not as good as a Rolex watch but darn close.

Take good care of this watch if you get one because it has gold plating on it. This watch is 'Not' a sport watch.

This watch features
-Rotating timer dial
-All stainless steel (kinda heavy)
-Glow in the dark
-Water resistant to 200 meters (600 feet)
-Automatic winding (from wrist movements)
-Shows date
-Very beautiful

Sizeing isn't difficult, I sized mine by using a thumbtack and a hammer to tap the pins out of the band and I tapped a pin back into the band after removing three band links. If you don't know what your doing then just take it to s jewelry store so they can size it for you

product_title: BOS Men's Automatic self-wind mechanical Pointer Skeleton Watch Black Dial Stainless Steel Band 9008
review_headline: The epitome of form before function.
review_body:
This is a beautiful watch. I love the look and feel of it, and I get complimented on it all the time. If that were the entirety of the story, this would be a 5 star review.

Unfortunately, the most important part of this watch, the functionality, has some issues. Despite this being an automatic winding watch, it doesn't always stay wound. I have had days where I had to re-wind it before the end of the day. Most days however, it does last through the day. I just have to wind it and set the time again in the morning. Other mechanical self winding watches I own will in fact not need to be wound again until I stop wearing them for a full day. In addition, I can't always get the spring fully wound before it will start clicking and the spring skips off the winding gear.

If I hadn't been so lazy, I would have returned this watch. Unfortunately, I missed the 30 day return window. So now I'm stuck with an only mostly working but beautiful watch. I guess that makes it kinda like a fashion model....

product_title: Invicta Men's 8926OB Pro Diver Stainless Steel Automatic Watch with Link Bracelet
review_headline: Worth the money, be careful with the glass.
review_body:
Alrighty, after seeking out the ultimate low-profile, ultra water resistant, mechanical watch with a rotating bezel and date for less than $100, I settled on this.

It looks much like the famous Rolex Submariner, and performs similarly.

However, after about a year of use now, the paint on the bezel is chipping, and after a decent smack on the hood of a car the crystal has cracked and all but shattered.

It keeps time fairly well, gaining about 15 seconds per day, without taking it to a healer for fine tuning.

product_title: Invicta Men's 8928OB Pro Diver Gold Stainless Steel Two-Tone Automatic Watch
review_body:
This watch is a very beautiful time piece. This also could be an alternative choice to a Rolex submariner. It also has the same features as a Rolex submariner but it's not as good as a Rolex watch but darn close.

Take good care of this watch if you get one because it has gold plating on it. This watch is 'Not' a sport watch.

This watch features
-Rotating timer dial
-All stainless steel (kinda heavy)
-Glow in the dark
-Water resistant to 200 meters (600 feet)
-Automatic winding (from wrist movements)
-Shows date
-Very beautiful

Sizeing isn't difficult, I sized mine by using a thumbtack and a hammer to tap the pins out of the band and I tapped a pin back into the band after removing three band links. If you don't know what your doing then just take it to s jewelry store so they can size it for you

product_title: BOS Men's Automatic self-wind mechanical Pointer Skeleton Watch Black Dial Stainless Steel Band 9008
review_headline: The epitome of form before function.
review_body:
This is a beautiful watch. I love the look and feel of it, and I get complimented on it all the time. If that were the entirety of the story, this would be a 5 star review.

Unfortunately, the most important part of this watch, the functionality, has some issues. Despite this being an automatic winding watch, it doesn't always stay wound. I have had days where I had to re-wind it before the end of the day. Most days however, it does last through the day. I just have to wind it and set the time again in the morning. Other mechanical self winding watches I own will in fact not need to be wound again until I stop wearing them for a full day. In addition, I can't always get the spring fully wound before it will start clicking and the spring skips off the winding gear.

If I hadn't been so lazy, I would have returned this watch. Unfortunately, I missed the 30 day return window. So now I'm stuck with an only mostly working but beautiful watch. I guess that makes it kinda like a fashion model....

product_title: Invicta Men's 8926OB Pro Diver Stainless Steel Automatic Watch with Link Bracelet
review_headline: Worth the money, be careful with the glass.
review_body:
Alrighty, after seeking out the ultimate low-profile, ultra water resistant, mechanical watch with a rotating bezel and date for less than $100, I settled on this.

It looks much like the famous Rolex Submariner, and performs similarly.

However, after about a year of use now, the paint on the bezel is chipping, and after a decent smack on the hood of a car the crystal has cracked and all but shattered.

It keeps time fairly well, gaining about 15 seconds per day, without taking it to a healer for fine tuning.

product_title: Invicta Men's 8928OB Pro Diver Gold Stainless Steel Two-Tone Automatic Watch
review_body:
This watch is a very beautiful time piece. This also could be an alternative choice to a Rolex submariner. It also has the same features as a Rolex submariner but it's not as good as a Rolex watch but darn close.

Take good care of this watch if you get one because it has gold plating on it. This watch is 'Not' a sport watch.

This watch features
-Rotating timer dial
-All stainless steel (kinda heavy)
-Glow in the dark
-Water resistant to 200 meters (600 feet)
-Automatic winding (from wrist movements)
-Shows date
-Very beautiful

Sizeing isn't difficult, I sized mine by using a thumbtack and a hammer to tap the pins out of the band and I tapped a pin back into the band after removing three band links. If you don't know what your doing then just take it to s jewelry store so they can size it for you

product_title: BOS Men's Automatic self-wind mechanical Pointer Skeleton Watch Black Dial Stainless Steel Band 9008
review_headline: The epitome of form before function.
review_body:
This is a beautiful watch. I love the look and feel of it, and I get complimented on it all the time. If that were the entirety of the story, this would be a 5 star review.

Unfortunately, the most important part of this watch, the functionality, has some issues. Despite this being an automatic winding watch, it doesn't always stay wound. I have had days where I had to re-wind it before the end of the day. Most days however, it does last through the day. I just have to wind it and set the time again in the morning. Other mechanical self winding watches I own will in fact not need to be wound again until I stop wearing them for a full day. In addition, I can't always get the spring fully wound before it will start clicking and the spring skips off the winding gear.

If I hadn't been so lazy, I would have returned this watch. Unfortunately, I missed the 30 day return window. So now I'm stuck with an only mostly working but beautiful watch. I guess that makes it kinda like a fashion model....

product_title: Invicta Men's 8926OB Pro Diver Stainless Steel Automatic Watch with Link Bracelet
review_headline: Worth the money, be careful with the glass.
review_body:
Alrighty, after seeking out the ultimate low-profile, ultra water resistant, mechanical watch with a rotating bezel and date for less than $100, I settled on this.

It looks much like the famous Rolex Submariner, and performs similarly.

However, after about a year of use now, the paint on the bezel is chipping, and after a decent smack on the hood of a car the crystal has cracked and all but shattered.

It keeps time fairly well, gaining about 15 seconds per day, without taking it to a healer for fine tuning.

review_body:
This watch is a very beautiful time piece. This also could be an alternative choice to a Rolex submariner. It also has the same features as a Rolex submariner but it's not as good as a Rolex watch but darn close.

Take good care of this watch if you get one because it has gold plating on it. This watch is 'Not' a sport watch.

This watch features
-Rotating timer dial
-All stainless steel (kinda heavy)
-Glow in the dark
-Water resistant to 200 meters (600 feet)
-Automatic winding (from wrist movements)
-Shows date
-Very beautiful

Sizeing isn't difficult, I sized mine by using a thumbtack and a hammer to tap the pins out of the band and I tapped a pin back into the band after removing three band links. If you don't know what your doing then just take it to s jewelry store so they can size it for you

product_title: BOS Men's Automatic self-wind mechanical Pointer Skeleton Watch Black Dial Stainless Steel Band 9008
review_headline: The epitome of form before function.
review_body:
This is a beautiful watch. I love the look and feel of it, and I get complimented on it all the time. If that were the entirety of the story, this would be a 5 star review.

Unfortunately, the most important part of this watch, the functionality, has some issues. Despite this being an automatic winding watch, it doesn't always stay wound. I have had days where I had to re-wind it before the end of the day. Most days however, it does last through the day. I just have to wind it and set the time again in the morning. Other mechanical self winding watches I own will in fact not need to be wound again until I stop wearing them for a full day. In addition, I can't always get the spring fully wound before it will start clicking and the spring skips off the winding gear.

If I hadn't been so lazy, I would have returned this watch. Unfortunately, I missed the 30 day return window. So now I'm stuck with an only mostly working but beautiful watch. I guess that makes it kinda like a fashion model....

product_title: Invicta Men's 8926OB Pro Diver Stainless Steel Automatic Watch with Link Bracelet
review_headline: Worth the money, be careful with the glass.
review_body:
Alrighty, after seeking out the ultimate low-profile, ultra water resistant, mechanical watch with a rotating bezel and date for less than $100, I settled on this.

It looks much like the famous Rolex Submariner, and performs similarly.

However, after about a year of use now, the paint on the bezel is chipping, and after a decent smack on the hood of a car the crystal has cracked and all but shattered.

It keeps time fairly well, gaining about 15 seconds per day, without taking it to a healer for fine tuning.

-Automatic winding (from wrist movements)

product_title: BOS Men's Automatic self-wind mechanical Pointer Skeleton Watch Black Dial Stainless Steel Band 9008
review_headline: The epitome of form before function.
review_body:
This is a beautiful watch. I love the look and feel of it, and I get complimented on it all the time. If that were the entirety of the story, this would be a 5 star review.

Unfortunately, the most important part of this watch, the functionality, has some issues. Despite this being an automatic winding watch, it doesn't always stay wound. I have had days where I had to re-wind it before the end of the day. Most days however, it does last through the day. I just have to wind it and set the time again in the morning. Other mechanical self winding watches I own will in fact not need to be wound again until I stop wearing them for a full day. In addition, I can't always get the spring fully wound before it will start clicking and the spring skips off the winding gear.

If I hadn't been so lazy, I would have returned this watch. Unfortunately, I missed the 30 day return window. So now I'm stuck with an only mostly working but beautiful watch. I guess that makes it kinda like a fashion model....

review_headline: Worth the money, be careful with the glass.
review_body:
Alrighty, after seeking out the ultimate low-profile, ultra water resistant, mechanical watch with a rotating bezel and date for less than $100, I settled on this.

It looks much like the famous Rolex Submariner, and performs similarly.

However, after about a year of use now, the paint on the bezel is chipping, and after a decent smack on the hood of a car the crystal has cracked and all but shattered.

It keeps time fairly well, gaining about 15 seconds per day, without taking it to a healer for fine tuning.

product_title: BOS Men's Automatic self-wind mechanical Pointer Skeleton Watch Black Dial Stainless Steel Band 9008
review_headline: The epitome of form before function.
review_body:
This is a beautiful watch. I love the look and feel of it, and I get complimented on it all the time. If that were the entirety of the story, this would be a 5 star review.

Unfortunately, the most important part of this watch, the functionality, has some issues. Despite this being an automatic winding watch, it doesn't always stay wound. I have had days where I had to re-wind it before the end of the day. Most days however, it does last through the day. I just have to wind it and set the time again in the morning. Other mechanical self winding watches I own will in fact not need to be wound again until I stop wearing them for a full day. In addition, I can't always get the spring fully wound before it will start clicking and the spring skips off the winding gear.

If I hadn't been so lazy, I would have returned this watch. Unfortunately, I missed the 30 day return window. So now I'm stuck with an only mostly working but beautiful watch. I guess that makes it kinda like a fashion model....

review_headline: Worth the money, be careful with the glass.
review_body:
Alrighty, after seeking out the ultimate low-profile, ultra water resistant, mechanical watch with a rotating bezel and date for less than $100, I settled on this.

It looks much like the famous Rolex Submariner, and performs similarly.

However, after about a year of use now, the paint on the bezel is chipping, and after a decent smack on the hood of a car the crystal has cracked and all but shattered.

It keeps time fairly well, gaining about 15 seconds per day, without taking it to a healer for fine tuning.

product_title: Invicta Men's 8928OB Pro Diver Gold Stainless Steel Two-Tone Automatic Watch
review_body:
This watch is a very beautiful time piece. This also could be an alternative choice to a Rolex submariner. It also has the same features as a Rolex submariner but it's not as good as a Rolex watch but darn close.

Take good care of this watch if you get one because it has gold plating on it. This watch is 'Not' a sport watch.

This watch features
-Rotating timer dial
-All stainless steel (kinda heavy)
-Glow in the dark
-Water resistant to 200 meters (600 feet)
-Automatic winding (from wrist movements)
-Shows date
-Very beautiful

Sizeing isn't difficult, I sized mine by using a thumbtack and a hammer to tap the pins out of the band and I tapped a pin back into the band after removing three band links. If you don't know what your doing then just take it to s jewelry store so they can size it for you

product_title: BOS Men's Automatic self-wind mechanical Pointer Skeleton Watch Black Dial Stainless Steel Band 9008
review_headline: The epitome of form before function.
review_body:
This is a beautiful watch. I love the look and feel of it, and I get complimented on it all the time. If that were the entirety of the story, this would be a 5 star review.

Unfortunately, the most important part of this watch, the functionality, has some issues. Despite this being an automatic winding watch, it doesn't always stay wound. I have had days where I had to re-wind it before the end of the day. Most days however, it does last through the day. I just have to wind it and set the time again in the morning. Other mechanical self winding watches I own will in fact not need to be wound again until I stop wearing them for a full day. In addition, I can't always get the spring fully wound before it will start clicking and the spring skips off the winding gear.

If I hadn't been so lazy, I would have returned this watch. Unfortunately, I missed the 30 day return window. So now I'm stuck with an only mostly working but beautiful watch. I guess that makes it kinda like a fashion model....

review_headline: Worth the money, be careful with the glass.
review_body:
Alrighty, after seeking out the ultimate low-profile, ultra water resistant, mechanical watch with a rotating bezel and date for less than $100, I settled on this.

It looks much like the famous Rolex Submariner, and performs similarly.

However, after about a year of use now, the paint on the bezel is chipping, and after a decent smack on the hood of a car the crystal has cracked and all but shattered.

It keeps time fairly well, gaining about 15 seconds per day, without taking it to a healer for fine tuning.

product_title: Invicta Men's 8928OB Pro Diver Gold Stainless Steel Two-Tone Automatic Watch
review_body:
This watch is a very beautiful time piece. This also could be an alternative choice to a Rolex submariner. It also has the same features as a Rolex submariner but it's not as good as a Rolex watch but darn close.

Take good care of this watch if you get one because it has gold plating on it. This watch is 'Not' a sport watch.

This watch features
-Rotating timer dial
-All stainless steel (kinda heavy)
-Glow in the dark
-Water resistant to 200 meters (600 feet)
-Automatic winding (from wrist movements)
-Shows date
-Very beautiful

Sizeing isn't difficult, I sized mine by using a thumbtack and a hammer to tap the pins out of the band and I tapped a pin back into the band after removing three band links. If you don't know what your doing then just take it to s jewelry store so they can size it for you

product_title: BOS Men's Automatic self-wind mechanical Pointer Skeleton Watch Black Dial Stainless Steel Band 9008
review_headline: The epitome of form before function.
review_body:
This is a beautiful watch. I love the look and feel of it, and I get complimented on it all the time. If that were the entirety of the story, this would be a 5 star review.

Unfortunately, the most important part of this watch, the functionality, has some issues. Despite this being an automatic winding watch, it doesn't always stay wound. I have had days where I had to re-wind it before the end of the day. Most days however, it does last through the day. I just have to wind it and set the time again in the morning. Other mechanical self winding watches I own will in fact not need to be wound again until I stop wearing them for a full day. In addition, I can't always get the spring fully wound before it will start clicking and the spring skips off the winding gear.

If I hadn't been so lazy, I would have returned this watch. Unfortunately, I missed the 30 day return window. So now I'm stuck with an only mostly working but beautiful watch. I guess that makes it kinda like a fashion model....

product_title: Invicta Men's 8926OB Pro Diver Stainless Steel Automatic Watch with Link Bracelet
review_headline: Worth the money, be careful with the glass.
review_body:
Alrighty, after seeking out the ultimate low-profile, ultra water resistant, mechanical watch with a rotating bezel and date for less than $100, I settled on this.

It looks much like the famous Rolex Submariner, and performs similarly.

However, after about a year of use now, the paint on the bezel is chipping, and after a decent smack on the hood of a car the crystal has cracked and all but shattered.

It keeps time fairly well, gaining about 15 seconds per day, without taking it to a healer for fine tuning.

review_headline: Beautiful statement piece, great quality, great price!
review_body: This is the first time I've ordered anything like this through Amazon. The photos that others posted in their reviews helped, but it is much nicer in person. The photos don't do it justice. It's a heavy piece, but not too heavy. It has the right weight to it for something with that many stones in it. If it was lighter, I would have worried about the quality - but this is not the case. For the price, this is perfect - probably even better than I expected! The stones have a lot of sparkle to them, but it's hard to get that in a photo. This is a striking piece.The necklace has varied shades of blue, so it could go with many different blue clothing pieces, or go well with something contrasting. The metal has an antique brass look to it. It looks like something you'd find in a higher end boutique.  I have no doubt this will be a great statement piece for everyday or for a special event look. I'm very glad I took a chance and bought this one. This was an awesome find! I can't say enough good things about it! If ...

product_title: Sterling Silver Infinity Twist Bead Dangle Earrings
review_headline: I bought both the silver and gold versions a couple of months ago.  Here is what I have learned...
review_body:
I bought both the 'silver' and 'gold' version of these earrings and kept both. I have had them for several months and here is why I like them:

They are lightweight. And they are comfortable and don't interfere with phone use or other things against my ears.

They are both classy and fun. I can wear them professionally to a work meeting, as well as out dancing. They can be dressed up or down. Basically this is a versatile earring that works for most outfits and occasions.

Lastly they are a bit unique. I get compliments on when I wear them! In sum - this is a great earring and I would recommend them. I hope this is helpful to you!

review_body:
The rings arrived with a velvet pouch and an alcohol swab for cleaning which was very nice. However, after one use, the stones started falling out. It was also disappointing to find out that I was injured after the first use. My nipples were very sore and I thought it was because I had not used them properly. After handling the rings more and looking closely, I noticed that there were metal tags on the ends of the rings that ended up cutting into my skin. I have a heavy duty file at home so I was able get in there and file down the tags.
They look really nice on when they have all the stones in.

product_title: Cavalier Jewelers 8MM Cobalt Chrome Ring Wedding Band - Flat Brushed Top and Polished Finish Edges
review_body:
I got married a few weeks ago and I really like this ring. My fiancee and I scoured around 15 different jewelry shops to look for our wedding bands. I noticed that the mens' bands made from alternative metals were very good in most shops , and in the range of 250-300 dollars. That's already a huge difference from what you'd pay for a white gold or platinum ring. However, most of these alternative metal bands displayed in the shops were size 10 (the standard display size) and given that these rings couldn't be resized they told me I would have to wait 1 or 2 weeks to order them.

That's how I started to check out rings online. All I really wanted was a clean, beveled cobalt ring. This ring by Cavalier looks just as good as those I've seen in the shops. The price is unbelievable. I prefer cobalt over tungsten because it has a brighter look that almost resembles white gold. This ring has a very nice texture and I kinda play with it often just as Gollum played with the Ring. I also quite like the fac...

review_headline: Beautiful statement piece, great quality, great price!
review_body: This is the first time I've ordered anything like this through Amazon. The photos that others posted in their reviews helped, but it is much nicer in person. The photos don't do it justice. It's a heavy piece, but not too heavy. It has the right weight to it for something with that many stones in it. If it was lighter, I would have worried about the quality - but this is not the case. For the price, this is perfect - probably even better than I expected! The stones have a lot of sparkle to them, but it's hard to get that in a photo. This is a striking piece.The necklace has varied shades of blue, so it could go with many different blue clothing pieces, or go well with something contrasting. The metal has an antique brass look to it. It looks like something you'd find in a higher end boutique.  I have no doubt this will be a great statement piece for everyday or for a special event look. I'm very glad I took a chance and bought this one. This was an awesome find! I can't say enough good things about it! If ...

review_body: I ordered the 6.5" rose gold, and it fits like a dream. I highly recommend taking a piece of string and measuring the circumference of your wrist before ordering. It is not too tight, nor large, has room to slide up my arm a few inches (to where my forearm starts). The color is great, shiny, and the screws tight. I love that the screws are connected to the bracelet, no fear of losing them-they're very small! One complaint I have, I ordered it with the ring, also in rose gold, and the ring is a yellow gold. I may order again to see if I get a better match.. I highly recommend this product, the engravings are inside, well made and super fast shipping (less then 1 week)

review_body:
The rings arrived with a velvet pouch and an alcohol swab for cleaning which was very nice. However, after one use, the stones started falling out. I was able to catch some or pull some out myself and super glue them in place but most of them have been lost. It was disappointing. It was also disappointing to find out that I was injured after the first use. My nipples were very sore and I thought it was because I had not used them properly. After handling the rings more and looking closely, I noticed that there were metal tags on the ends of the rings that ended up cutting into my skin. I have a heavy duty file at home so I was able get in there and file down the tags.
They look really nice on when they have all the stones in.

product_title: Cavalier Jewelers 8MM Cobalt Chrome Ring Wedding Band - Flat Brushed Top and Polished Finish Edges
review_body:
I got married a few weeks ago and I really like this ring. My fiancee and I scoured around 15 different jewelry shops to look for our wedding bands. I noticed that the mens' bands made from alternative metals were very good in most shops , and in the range of 250-300 dollars. That's already a huge difference from what you'd pay for a white gold or platinum ring. However, most of these alternative metal bands displayed in the shops were size 10 (the standard display size) and given that these rings couldn't be resized they told me I would have to wait 1 or 2 weeks to order them.

That's how I started to check out rings online. All I really wanted was a clean, beveled cobalt ring. This ring by Cavalier looks just as good as those I've seen in the shops. The price is unbelievable. I prefer cobalt over tungsten because it has a brighter look that almost resembles white gold. This ring has a very nice texture and I kinda play with it often just as Gollum played with the Ring. I also quite like the fac...

review_headline: Beautiful statement piece, great quality, great price!
review_body: This is the first time I've ordered anything like this through Amazon. The photos that others posted in their reviews helped, but it is much nicer in person. The photos don't do it justice. It's a heavy piece, but not too heavy. It has the right weight to it for something with that many stones in it. If it was lighter, I would have worried about the quality - but this is not the case. For the price, this is perfect - probably even better than I expected! The stones have a lot of sparkle to them, but it's hard to get that in a photo. This is a striking piece.The necklace has varied shades of blue, so it could go with many different blue clothing pieces, or go well with something contrasting. The metal has an antique brass look to it. It looks like something you'd find in a higher end boutique.  I have no doubt this will be a great statement piece for everyday or for a special event look. I'm very glad I took a chance and bought this one. This was an awesome find! I can't say enough good things about it! If ...

product_title: Sterling Silver Infinity Twist Bead Dangle Earrings
review_headline: I bought both the silver and gold versions a couple of months ago.  Here is what I have learned...
review_body:
I bought both the 'silver' and 'gold' version of these earrings and kept both. I have had them for several months and here is why I like them:

They are lightweight. And they are comfortable and don't interfere with phone use or other things against my ears.

They are both classy and fun. I can wear them professionally to a work meeting, as well as out dancing. They can be dressed up or down. Basically this is a versatile earring that works for most outfits and occasions.

Lastly they are a bit unique. I get compliments on when I wear them! In sum - this is a great earring and I would recommend them. I hope this is helpful to you!

product_title: Cavalier Jewelers 8MM Cobalt Chrome Ring Wedding Band - Flat Brushed Top and Polished Finish Edges
review_body:
I got married a few weeks ago and I really like this ring. My fiancee and I scoured around 15 different jewelry shops to look for our wedding bands. I noticed that the mens' bands made from alternative metals were very good in most shops , and in the range of 250-300 dollars. That's already a huge difference from what you'd pay for a white gold or platinum ring. However, most of these alternative metal bands displayed in the shops were size 10 (the standard display size) and given that these rings couldn't be resized they told me I would have to wait 1 or 2 weeks to order them.

That's how I started to check out rings online. All I really wanted was a clean, beveled cobalt ring. This ring by Cavalier looks just as good as those I've seen in the shops. The price is unbelievable. I prefer cobalt over tungsten because it has a brighter look that almost resembles white gold. This ring has a very nice texture and I kinda play with it often just as Gollum played with the Ring. I also quite like the fac...

review_headline: Beautiful statement piece, great quality, great price!
review_body: This is the first time I've ordered anything like this through Amazon. The photos that others posted in their reviews helped, but it is much nicer in person. The photos don't do it justice. It's a heavy piece, but not too heavy. It has the right weight to it for something with that many stones in it. If it was lighter, I would have worried about the quality - but this is not the case. For the price, this is perfect - probably even better than I expected! The stones have a lot of sparkle to them, but it's hard to get that in a photo. This is a striking piece.The necklace has varied shades of blue, so it could go with many different blue clothing pieces, or go well with something contrasting. The metal has an antique brass look to it. It looks like something you'd find in a higher end boutique.  I have no doubt this will be a great statement piece for everyday or for a special event look. I'm very glad I took a chance and bought this one. This was an awesome find! I can't say enough good things about it! If ...

product_title: Sterling Silver Infinity Twist Bead Dangle Earrings
review_headline: I bought both the silver and gold versions a couple of months ago.  Here is what I have learned...
review_body:
I bought both the 'silver' and 'gold' version of these earrings and kept both. I have had them for several months and here is why I like them:

They are lightweight. And they are comfortable and don't interfere with phone use or other things against my ears.

They are both classy and fun. I can wear them professionally to a work meeting, as well as out dancing. They can be dressed up or down. Basically this is a versatile earring that works for most outfits and occasions.

Lastly they are a bit unique. I get compliments on when I wear them! In sum - this is a great earring and I would recommend them. I hope this is helpful to you!

I got married a few weeks ago and I really like this ring. My fiancee and I scoured around 15 different jewelry shops to look for our wedding bands. I noticed that the mens' bands made from alternative metals were very good in most shops , and in the range of 250-300 dollars. That's already a huge difference from what you'd pay for a white gold or platinum ring. However, most of these alternative metal bands displayed in the shops were size 10 (the standard display size) and given that these rings couldn't be resized they told me I would have to wait 1 or 2 weeks to order them.

That's how I started to check out rings online. All I really wanted was a clean, beveled cobalt ring. This ring by Cavalier looks just as good as those I've seen in the shops. The price is unbelievable. I prefer cobalt over tungsten because it has a brighter look that almost resembles white gold. This ring has a very nice texture and I kinda play with it often just as Gollum played with the Ring. I also quite like the fac...

review_headline: Beautiful statement piece, great quality, great price!
review_body: This is the first time I've ordered anything like this through Amazon. The photos that others posted in their reviews helped, but it is much nicer in person. The photos don't do it justice. It's a heavy piece, but not too heavy. It has the right weight to it for something with that many stones in it. If it was lighter, I would have worried about the quality - but this is not the case. For the price, this is perfect - probably even better than I expected! The stones have a lot of sparkle to them, but it's hard to get that in a photo. This is a striking piece.The necklace has varied shades of blue, so it could go with many different blue clothing pieces, or go well with something contrasting. The metal has an antique brass look to it. It looks like something you'd find in a higher end boutique.  I have no doubt this will be a great statement piece for everyday or for a special event look. I'm very glad I took a chance and bought this one. This was an awesome find! I can't say enough good things about it! If ...

product_title: Sterling Silver Infinity Twist Bead Dangle Earrings
review_headline: I bought both the silver and gold versions a couple of months ago.  Here is what I have learned...
review_body:
I bought both the 'silver' and 'gold' version of these earrings and kept both. I have had them for several months and here is why I like them:

They are lightweight. And they are comfortable and don't interfere with phone use or other things against my ears.

They are both classy and fun. I can wear them professionally to a work meeting, as well as out dancing. They can be dressed up or down. Basically this is a versatile earring that works for most outfits and occasions.

Lastly they are a bit unique. I get compliments on when I wear them! In sum - this is a great earring and I would recommend them. I hope this is helpful to you!

As someone mentioned, the pendant is smaller than it seems from the pictures but my wife prefers subtlety. You can't exactly tell it's a heart-shaped stone unless you get up close. The included chain necklace seems to be of good quality. It's quite thin and the clasp is a bit small. For the first few days after giving it to her, I had to help her put it on. She tends to have longer fingernails so releasing the clasp was a little tough with it being so small. I had no issues though.

review_headline: Beautiful statement piece, great quality, great price!
review_body: This is the first time I've ordered anything like this through Amazon. The photos that others posted in their reviews helped, but it is much nicer in person. The photos don't do it justice. It's a heavy piece, but not too heavy. It has the right weight to it for something with that many stones in it. If it was lighter, I would have worried about the quality - but this is not the case. For the price, this is perfect - probably even better than I expected! The stones have a lot of sparkle to them, but it's hard to get that in a photo. This is a striking piece.The necklace has varied shades of blue, so it could go with many different blue clothing pieces, or go well with something contrasting. The metal has an antique brass look to it. It looks like something you'd find in a higher end boutique.  I have no doubt this will be a great statement piece for everyday or for a special event look. I'm very glad I took a chance and bought this one. This was an awesome find! I can't say enough good things about it! If ...

product_title: Sterling Silver Infinity Twist Bead Dangle Earrings
review_headline: I bought both the silver and gold versions a couple of months ago.  Here is what I have learned...
review_body:
I bought both the 'silver' and 'gold' version of these earrings and kept both. I have had them for several months and here is why I like them:

They are lightweight. And they are comfortable and don't interfere with phone use or other things against my ears.

They are both classy and fun. I can wear them professionally to a work meeting, as well as out dancing. They can be dressed up or down. Basically this is a versatile earring that works for most outfits and occasions.

Lastly they are a bit unique. I get compliments on when I wear them! In sum - this is a great earring and I would recommend them. I hope this is helpful to you!

product_title: A Pair Nipple rings Flower shape Nickel free nipple shield Copper fashion women body piercing jewelry
review_body:
The rings arrived with a velvet pouch and an alcohol swab for cleaning which was very nice. However, after one use, the stones started falling out. I was able to catch some or pull some out myself and super glue them in place but most of them have been lost. It was disappointing. It was also disappointing to find out that I was injured after the first use. My nipples were very sore and I thought it was because I had not used them properly. After handling the rings more and looking closely, I noticed that there were metal tags on the ends of the rings that ended up cutting into my skin. I have a heavy duty file at home so I was able get in there and file down the tags.
They look really nice on when they have all the stones in.

product_title: Cavalier Jewelers 8MM Cobalt Chrome Ring Wedding Band - Flat Brushed Top and Polished Finish Edges
review_body:
I got married a few weeks ago and I really like this ring. My fiancee and I scoured around 15 different jewelry shops to look for our wedding bands. I noticed that the mens' bands made from alternative metals were very good in most shops , and in the range of 250-300 dollars. That's already a huge difference from what you'd pay for a white gold or platinum ring. However, most of these alternative metal bands displayed in the shops were size 10 (the standard display size) and given that these rings couldn't be resized they told me I would have to wait 1 or 2 weeks to order them.

That's how I started to check out rings online. All I really wanted was a clean, beveled cobalt ring. This ring by Cavalier looks just as good as those I've seen in the shops. The price is unbelievable. I prefer cobalt over tungsten because it has a brighter look that almost resembles white gold. This ring has a very nice texture and I kinda play with it often just as Gollum played with the Ring. I also quite like the fac...

product_title: Fun Daisy New Design Jewelry Vintage Grand Choker Rhinestones Fashion Necklace
review_headline: Beautiful statement piece, great quality, great price!
review_body: This is the first time I've ordered anything like this through Amazon. The photos that others posted in their reviews helped, but it is much nicer in person. The photos don't do it justice. It's a heavy piece, but not too heavy. It has the right weight to it for something with that many stones in it. If it was lighter, I would have worried about the quality - but this is not the case. For the price, this is perfect - probably even better than I expected! The stones have a lot of sparkle to them, but it's hard to get that in a photo. This is a striking piece.The necklace has varied shades of blue, so it could go with many different blue clothing pieces, or go well with something contrasting. The metal has an antique brass look to it. It looks like something you'd find in a higher end boutique.  I have no doubt this will be a great statement piece for everyday or for a special event look. I'm very glad I took a chance and bought this one. This was an awesome find! I can't say enough good things about it! If ...

product_title: Sterling Silver Infinity Twist Bead Dangle Earrings
review_headline: I bought both the silver and gold versions a couple of months ago.  Here is what I have learned...
review_body:
I bought both the 'silver' and 'gold' version of these earrings and kept both. I have had them for several months and here is why I like them:

They are lightweight. And they are comfortable and don't interfere with phone use or other things against my ears.

They are both classy and fun. I can wear them professionally to a work meeting, as well as out dancing. They can be dressed up or down. Basically this is a versatile earring that works for most outfits and occasions.

Lastly they are a bit unique. I get compliments on when I wear them! In sum - this is a great earring and I would recommend them. I hope this is helpful to you!

product_title: A Pair Nipple rings Flower shape Nickel free nipple shield Copper fashion women body piercing jewelry
review_body:
The rings arrived with a velvet pouch and an alcohol swab for cleaning which was very nice. However, after one use, the stones started falling out. I was able to catch some or pull some out myself and super glue them in place but most of them have been lost. It was disappointing. It was also disappointing to find out that I was injured after the first use. My nipples were very sore and I thought it was because I had not used them properly. After handling the rings more and looking closely, I noticed that there were metal tags on the ends of the rings that ended up cutting into my skin. I have a heavy duty file at home so I was able get in there and file down the tags.
They look really nice on when they have all the stones in.

product_title: Cavalier Jewelers 8MM Cobalt Chrome Ring Wedding Band - Flat Brushed Top and Polished Finish Edges
review_body:
I got married a few weeks ago and I really like this ring. My fiancee and I scoured around 15 different jewelry shops to look for our wedding bands. I noticed that the mens' bands made from alternative metals were very good in most shops , and in the range of 250-300 dollars. That's already a huge difference from what you'd pay for a white gold or platinum ring. However, most of these alternative metal bands displayed in the shops were size 10 (the standard display size) and given that these rings couldn't be resized they told me I would have to wait 1 or 2 weeks to order them.

That's how I started to check out rings online. All I really wanted was a clean, beveled cobalt ring. This ring by Cavalier looks just as good as those I've seen in the shops. The price is unbelievable. I prefer cobalt over tungsten because it has a brighter look that almost resembles white gold. This ring has a very nice texture and I kinda play with it often just as Gollum played with the Ring. I also quite like the fac...

They are lightweight. And they are comfortable and don't interfere with phone use or other things against my ears.

They are both classy and fun. I can wear them professionally to a work meeting, as well as out dancing. They can be dressed up or down. Basically this is a versatile earring that works for most outfits and occasions.

product_title: Cavalier Jewelers 8MM Cobalt Chrome Ring Wedding Band - Flat Brushed Top and Polished Finish Edges
review_body:
I got married a few weeks ago and I really like this ring. My fiancee and I scoured around 15 different jewelry shops to look for our wedding bands. I noticed that the mens' bands made from alternative metals were very good in most shops , and in the range of 250-300 dollars. That's already a huge difference from what you'd pay for a white gold or platinum ring. However, most of these alternative metal bands displayed in the shops were size 10 (the standard display size) and given that these rings couldn't be resized they told me I would have to wait 1 or 2 weeks to order them.

That's how I started to check out rings online. All I really wanted was a clean, beveled cobalt ring. This ring by Cavalier looks just as good as those I've seen in the shops. The price is unbelievable. I prefer cobalt over tungsten because it has a brighter look that almost resembles white gold. This ring has a very nice texture and I kinda play with it often just as Gollum played with the Ring. I also quite like the fac...

product_title: Sterling Silver Infinity Twist Bead Dangle Earrings
review_headline: I bought both the silver and gold versions a couple of months ago.  Here is what I have learned...
review_body:
I bought both the 'silver' and 'gold' version of these earrings and kept both. I have had them for several months and here is why I like them:

They are lightweight. And they are comfortable and don't interfere with phone use or other things against my ears.

They are both classy and fun. I can wear them professionally to a work meeting, as well as out dancing. They can be dressed up or down. Basically this is a versatile earring that works for most outfits and occasions.

Lastly they are a bit unique. I get compliments on when I wear them! In sum - this is a great earring and I would recommend them. I hope this is helpful to you!

product_title: Cavalier Jewelers 8MM Cobalt Chrome Ring Wedding Band - Flat Brushed Top and Polished Finish Edges
review_body:
I got married a few weeks ago and I really like this ring. My fiancee and I scoured around 15 different jewelry shops to look for our wedding bands. I noticed that the mens' bands made from alternative metals were very good in most shops , and in the range of 250-300 dollars. That's already a huge difference from what you'd pay for a white gold or platinum ring. However, most of these alternative metal bands displayed in the shops were size 10 (the standard display size) and given that these rings couldn't be resized they told me I would have to wait 1 or 2 weeks to order them.

That's how I started to check out rings online. All I really wanted was a clean, beveled cobalt ring. This ring by Cavalier looks just as good as those I've seen in the shops. The price is unbelievable. I prefer cobalt over tungsten because it has a brighter look that almost resembles white gold. This ring has a very nice texture and I kinda play with it often just as Gollum played with the Ring. I also quite like the fac...

review_headline: Beautiful statement piece, great quality, great price!
review_body: This is the first time I've ordered anything like this through Amazon. The photos that others posted in their reviews helped, but it is much nicer in person. The photos don't do it justice. It's a heavy piece, but not too heavy. It has the right weight to it for something with that many stones in it. If it was lighter, I would have worried about the quality - but this is not the case. For the price, this is perfect - probably even better than I expected! The stones have a lot of sparkle to them, but it's hard to get that in a photo. This is a striking piece.The necklace has varied shades of blue, so it could go with many different blue clothing pieces, or go well with something contrasting. The metal has an antique brass look to it. It looks like something you'd find in a higher end boutique.  I have no doubt this will be a great statement piece for everyday or for a special event look. I'm very glad I took a chance and bought this one. This was an awesome find! I can't say enough good things about it! If ...

I love that the screws are connected to the bracelet, no fear of losing them-they're very small! One complaint I have, I ordered it with the ring, also in rose gold, and the ring is a yellow gold. review_body:
I got married a few weeks ago and I really like this ring. My fiancee and I scoured around 15 different jewelry shops to look for our wedding bands. I noticed that the mens' bands made from alternative metals were very good in most shops , and in the range of 250-300 dollars. That's already a huge difference from what you'd pay for a white gold or platinum ring. However, most of these alternative metal bands displayed in the shops were size 10 (the standard display size) and given that these rings couldn't be resized they told me I would have to wait 1 or 2 weeks to order them.

That's how I started to check out rings online. All I really wanted was a clean, beveled cobalt ring. This ring by Cavalier looks just as good as those I've seen in the shops. The price is unbelievable. I prefer cobalt over tungsten because it has a brighter look that almost resembles white gold. This ring has a very nice texture and I kinda play with it often just as Gollum played with the Ring. I also quite like the fac...

product_title: Polare Manly Real Thick Cowhide Leather Weekender Travel Gym Duffel Bag
review_headline: Strong well-made leather bag, but poor choice of pockets clasps.
review_body:
I've had this bag for a couple of weeks now and just took it on my first weekend away.
Firstly, the good: the leather is excellent quality full grain oiled leather that looks like it will last a lifetime of knocks. The stitching, workmanship and hardware all appear to be good quality. It's not a huge bag, but big enough for a weekend if you travel light. Fits easily into plane overhead lockers.
The neutral: the buckles for access into the main compartment are strong and will definitely last longer than any zipper would. However they don't provide easy access into the body of the bag if you need something quickly and obviously don't completely seal the bag from the outside as a zipper would.
The bad: the magnetic clasps on the outside pockets. The clasps are not at all secure and readily unfasten when you don't want them to. They will unfasten when the bag brushes against anything like a chair, armrest or other luggage in the overhead compartment, or even when it tangles with its own s...

review_headline: Great organizer for the abyss (a purse)
review_body: Fits well in my purse and makes organizing much easier.  For some reason, I have no idea why, I usually am unable to find things easily in my purses.  I don't carry a huge bag with everything but the kitchen sink in my purse, just the normal stuff, money, chapstick, compact brush, checkbooks, emergency feminine hygiene products, gum, some medications in small containers, car keys, etc.  Everything would always get lost in my purse and I'd have to dig around to find stuff.  Well, since getting this, I no longer have to search forever for things I need to retrieve.  This has several pockets to hold smaller items from getting lost at the bottom of your purse, a main compartment that is large enough to hold the things I need to carry, an outside zippered pocket, a mini flashlight, a flat bottom to stand up on it's own, and two small handles making it easy to take out of one purse and stick into another.  I purchased this just before a trip and it has been a lifesaver.

review_body: I purchased this bag for a trip to Europe, and it worked splendidly. This bag is really nice looking, sturdy and yet lightweight enough to be carried all day. product_title: Polare Manly Real Thick Cowhide Leather Weekender Travel Gym Duffel Bag
review_headline: Strong well-made leather bag, but poor choice of pockets clasps.
review_body:
I've had this bag for a couple of weeks now and just took it on my first weekend away.
Firstly, the good: the leather is excellent quality full grain oiled leather that looks like it will last a lifetime of knocks. The stitching, workmanship and hardware all appear to be good quality. It's not a huge bag, but big enough for a weekend if you travel light. Fits easily into plane overhead lockers.
The neutral: the buckles for access into the main compartment are strong and will definitely last longer than any zipper would. However they don't provide easy access into the body of the bag if you need something quickly and obviously don't completely seal the bag from the outside as a zipper would.
The bad: the magnetic clasps on the outside pockets. The clasps are not at all secure and readily unfasten when you don't want them to. They will unfasten when the bag brushes against anything like a chair, armrest or other luggage in the overhead compartment, or even when it tangles with its own s...

review_headline: Great organizer for the abyss (a purse)
review_body: Fits well in my purse and makes organizing much easier.  For some reason, I have no idea why, I usually am unable to find things easily in my purses.  I don't carry a huge bag with everything but the kitchen sink in my purse, just the normal stuff, money, chapstick, compact brush, checkbooks, emergency feminine hygiene products, gum, some medications in small containers, car keys, etc.  Everything would always get lost in my purse and I'd have to dig around to find stuff.  Well, since getting this, I no longer have to search forever for things I need to retrieve.  This has several pockets to hold smaller items from getting lost at the bottom of your purse, a main compartment that is large enough to hold the things I need to carry, an outside zippered pocket, a mini flashlight, a flat bottom to stand up on it's own, and two small handles making it easy to take out of one purse and stick into another.  I purchased this just before a trip and it has been a lifesaver.

product_title: Polare Manly Real Thick Cowhide Leather Weekender Travel Gym Duffel Bag
review_headline: Strong well-made leather bag, but poor choice of pockets clasps.
review_body:
I've had this bag for a couple of weeks now and just took it on my first weekend away.
Firstly, the good: the leather is excellent quality full grain oiled leather that looks like it will last a lifetime of knocks. The stitching, workmanship and hardware all appear to be good quality. It's not a huge bag, but big enough for a weekend if you travel light. Fits easily into plane overhead lockers.
The neutral: the buckles for access into the main compartment are strong and will definitely last longer than any zipper would. However they don't provide easy access into the body of the bag if you need something quickly and obviously don't completely seal the bag from the outside as a zipper would.
The bad: the magnetic clasps on the outside pockets. The clasps are not at all secure and readily unfasten when you don't want them to. They will unfasten when the bag brushes against anything like a chair, armrest or other luggage in the overhead compartment, or even when it tangles with its own s...

review_headline: Great organizer for the abyss (a purse)
review_body: Fits well in my purse and makes organizing much easier.  For some reason, I have no idea why, I usually am unable to find things easily in my purses.  I don't carry a huge bag with everything but the kitchen sink in my purse, just the normal stuff, money, chapstick, compact brush, checkbooks, emergency feminine hygiene products, gum, some medications in small containers, car keys, etc.  Everything would always get lost in my purse and I'd have to dig around to find stuff.  Well, since getting this, I no longer have to search forever for things I need to retrieve.  This has several pockets to hold smaller items from getting lost at the bottom of your purse, a main compartment that is large enough to hold the things I need to carry, an outside zippered pocket, a mini flashlight, a flat bottom to stand up on it's own, and two small handles making it easy to take out of one purse and stick into another. review_headline: Great organizer for the abyss (a purse)
review_body: Fits well in my purse and makes organizing much easier.  For some reason, I have no idea why, I usually am unable to find things easily in my purses.  I don't carry a huge bag with everything but the kitchen sink in my purse, just the normal stuff, money, chapstick, compact brush, checkbooks, emergency feminine hygiene products, gum, some medications in small containers, car keys, etc.  Everything would always get lost in my purse and I'd have to dig around to find stuff.  Well, since getting this, I no longer have to search forever for things I need to retrieve.  This has several pockets to hold smaller items from getting lost at the bottom of your purse, a main compartment that is large enough to hold the things I need to carry, an outside zippered pocket, a mini flashlight, a flat bottom to stand up on it's own, and two small handles making it easy to take out of one purse and stick into another.  I purchased this just before a trip and it has been a lifesaver.

product_title: Polare Manly Real Thick Cowhide Leather Weekender Travel Gym Duffel Bag
review_headline: Strong well-made leather bag, but poor choice of pockets clasps.
review_body:
I've had this bag for a couple of weeks now and just took it on my first weekend away.
Firstly, the good: the leather is excellent quality full grain oiled leather that looks like it will last a lifetime of knocks. The stitching, workmanship and hardware all appear to be good quality. It's not a huge bag, but big enough for a weekend if you travel light. Fits easily into plane overhead lockers.
The neutral: the buckles for access into the main compartment are strong and will definitely last longer than any zipper would. However they don't provide easy access into the body of the bag if you need something quickly and obviously don't completely seal the bag from the outside as a zipper would.
The bad: the magnetic clasps on the outside pockets. The clasps are not at all secure and readily unfasten when you don't want them to. They will unfasten when the bag brushes against anything like a chair, armrest or other luggage in the overhead compartment, or even when it tangles with its own s...

product_title: Polare Manly Real Thick Cowhide Leather Weekender Travel Gym Duffel Bag
review_headline: Strong well-made leather bag, but poor choice of pockets clasps.
review_body:
I've had this bag for a couple of weeks now and just took it on my first weekend away.
Firstly, the good: the leather is excellent quality full grain oiled leather that looks like it will last a lifetime of knocks. The stitching, workmanship and hardware all appear to be good quality. It's not a huge bag, but big enough for a weekend if you travel light. Fits easily into plane overhead lockers.
The neutral: the buckles for access into the main compartment are strong and will definitely last longer than any zipper would. However they don't provide easy access into the body of the bag if you need something quickly and obviously don't completely seal the bag from the outside as a zipper would.
The bad: the magnetic clasps on the outside pockets. The clasps are not at all secure and readily unfasten when you don't want them to. They will unfasten when the bag brushes against anything like a chair, armrest or other luggage in the overhead compartment, or even when it tangles with its own s...

review_headline: Great organizer for the abyss (a purse)
review_body: Fits well in my purse and makes organizing much easier.  For some reason, I have no idea why, I usually am unable to find things easily in my purses.  I don't carry a huge bag with everything but the kitchen sink in my purse, just the normal stuff, money, chapstick, compact brush, checkbooks, emergency feminine hygiene products, gum, some medications in small containers, car keys, etc.  Everything would always get lost in my purse and I'd have to dig around to find stuff.  Well, since getting this, I no longer have to search forever for things I need to retrieve.  This has several pockets to hold smaller items from getting lost at the bottom of your purse, a main compartment that is large enough to hold the things I need to carry, an outside zippered pocket, a mini flashlight, a flat bottom to stand up on it's own, and two small handles making it easy to take out of one purse and stick into another.  I purchased this just before a trip and it has been a lifesaver.

product_title: Polare Manly Real Thick Cowhide Leather Weekender Travel Gym Duffel Bag
review_headline: Strong well-made leather bag, but poor choice of pockets clasps.
review_body:
I've had this bag for a couple of weeks now and just took it on my first weekend away.
Firstly, the good: the leather is excellent quality full grain oiled leather that looks like it will last a lifetime of knocks. The stitching, workmanship and hardware all appear to be good quality. It's not a huge bag, but big enough for a weekend if you travel light. Fits easily into plane overhead lockers.
The neutral: the buckles for access into the main compartment are strong and will definitely last longer than any zipper would. However they don't provide easy access into the body of the bag if you need something quickly and obviously don't completely seal the bag from the outside as a zipper would.
The bad: the magnetic clasps on the outside pockets. The clasps are not at all secure and readily unfasten when you don't want them to. They will unfasten when the bag brushes against anything like a chair, armrest or other luggage in the overhead compartment, or even when it tangles with its own s...

review_headline: Great organizer for the abyss (a purse)
review_body: Fits well in my purse and makes organizing much easier.  For some reason, I have no idea why, I usually am unable to find things easily in my purses.  I don't carry a huge bag with everything but the kitchen sink in my purse, just the normal stuff, money, chapstick, compact brush, checkbooks, emergency feminine hygiene products, gum, some medications in small containers, car keys, etc.  Everything would always get lost in my purse and I'd have to dig around to find stuff.  Well, since getting this, I no longer have to search forever for things I need to retrieve.  This has several pockets to hold smaller items from getting lost at the bottom of your purse, a main compartment that is large enough to hold the things I need to carry, an outside zippered pocket, a mini flashlight, a flat bottom to stand up on it's own, and two small handles making it easy to take out of one purse and stick into another.  I purchased this just before a trip and it has been a lifesaver.

product_title: Sherpani Trevia Cross Body Tote
review_body: I purchased this bag for a trip to Europe, and it worked splendidly. I specifically wanted a cross-body bag for security that also had carry handles and a front zipped pocket for easy access to my phone.  This bag is really nice looking, sturdy and yet lightweight enough to be carried all day. The interior pockets were great for passports and sun glasses and the main pocket was big enough to hold multiple items including a water bottle. I used the small magnetic closing pocket on the front for lotion, makeup and tissues, and the back slip pocket was great for museum and train tickets.  This has definitely become my favorite travel bag. Very highly recommended!

product_title: Polare Manly Real Thick Cowhide Leather Weekender Travel Gym Duffel Bag
review_headline: Strong well-made leather bag, but poor choice of pockets clasps.
review_body:
I've had this bag for a couple of weeks now and just took it on my first weekend away.
Firstly, the good: the leather is excellent quality full grain oiled leather that looks like it will last a lifetime of knocks. The stitching, workmanship and hardware all appear to be good quality. It's not a huge bag, but big enough for a weekend if you travel light. Fits easily into plane overhead lockers.
The neutral: the buckles for access into the main compartment are strong and will definitely last longer than any zipper would. However they don't provide easy access into the body of the bag if you need something quickly and obviously don't completely seal the bag from the outside as a zipper would.
The bad: the magnetic clasps on the outside pockets. The clasps are not at all secure and readily unfasten when you don't want them to. They will unfasten when the bag brushes against anything like a chair, armrest or other luggage in the overhead compartment, or even when it tangles with its own s...

product_title: Travelon Rfid Blocking Purse Organizer
review_headline: Great organizer for the abyss (a purse)
review_body: Fits well in my purse and makes organizing much easier.  For some reason, I have no idea why, I usually am unable to find things easily in my purses.  I don't carry a huge bag with everything but the kitchen sink in my purse, just the normal stuff, money, chapstick, compact brush, checkbooks, emergency feminine hygiene products, gum, some medications in small containers, car keys, etc.  Everything would always get lost in my purse and I'd have to dig around to find stuff.  Well, since getting this, I no longer have to search forever for things I need to retrieve.  This has several pockets to hold smaller items from getting lost at the bottom of your purse, a main compartment that is large enough to hold the things I need to carry, an outside zippered pocket, a mini flashlight, a flat bottom to stand up on it's own, and two small handles making it easy to take out of one purse and stick into another.  I purchased this just before a trip and it has been a lifesaver.

product_title: Sherpani Trevia Cross Body Tote
review_body: I purchased this bag for a trip to Europe, and it worked splendidly. I specifically wanted a cross-body bag for security that also had carry handles and a front zipped pocket for easy access to my phone.  This bag is really nice looking, sturdy and yet lightweight enough to be carried all day. The interior pockets were great for passports and sun glasses and the main pocket was big enough to hold multiple items including a water bottle. I used the small magnetic closing pocket on the front for lotion, makeup and tissues, and the back slip pocket was great for museum and train tickets.  This has definitely become my favorite travel bag. Very highly recommended!

product_title: Polare Manly Real Thick Cowhide Leather Weekender Travel Gym Duffel Bag
review_headline: Strong well-made leather bag, but poor choice of pockets clasps.
review_body:
I've had this bag for a couple of weeks now and just took it on my first weekend away.
Firstly, the good: the leather is excellent quality full grain oiled leather that looks like it will last a lifetime of knocks. The stitching, workmanship and hardware all appear to be good quality. It's not a huge bag, but big enough for a weekend if you travel light. Fits easily into plane overhead lockers.
The neutral: the buckles for access into the main compartment are strong and will definitely last longer than any zipper would. However they don't provide easy access into the body of the bag if you need something quickly and obviously don't completely seal the bag from the outside as a zipper would.
The bad: the magnetic clasps on the outside pockets. The clasps are not at all secure and readily unfasten when you don't want them to. They will unfasten when the bag brushes against anything like a chair, armrest or other luggage in the overhead compartment, or even when it tangles with its own s...

review_headline: Great organizer for the abyss (a purse)
review_body: Fits well in my purse and makes organizing much easier.  For some reason, I have no idea why, I usually am unable to find things easily in my purses.  I don't carry a huge bag with everything but the kitchen sink in my purse, just the normal stuff, money, chapstick, compact brush, checkbooks, emergency feminine hygiene products, gum, some medications in small containers, car keys, etc.  Everything would always get lost in my purse and I'd have to dig around to find stuff.  Well, since getting this, I no longer have to search forever for things I need to retrieve.  This has several pockets to hold smaller items from getting lost at the bottom of your purse, a main compartment that is large enough to hold the things I need to carry, an outside zippered pocket, a mini flashlight, a flat bottom to stand up on it's own, and two small handles making it easy to take out of one purse and stick into another.  I purchased this just before a trip and it has been a lifesaver.

review_headline: Great organizer for the abyss (a purse)
review_body: Fits well in my purse and makes organizing much easier.  For some reason, I have no idea why, I usually am unable to find things easily in my purses.  I don't carry a huge bag with everything but the kitchen sink in my purse, just the normal stuff, money, chapstick, compact brush, checkbooks, emergency feminine hygiene products, gum, some medications in small containers, car keys, etc.  Everything would always get lost in my purse and I'd have to dig around to find stuff.  Well, since getting this, I no longer have to search forever for things I need to retrieve.  This has several pockets to hold smaller items from getting lost at the bottom of your purse, a main compartment that is large enough to hold the things I need to carry, an outside zippered pocket, a mini flashlight, a flat bottom to stand up on it's own, and two small handles making it easy to take out of one purse and stick into another.  I purchased this just before a trip and it has been a lifesaver.

product_title: Amazon.com Gift Cards, Pack of 3 (Various Designs)
review_headline: Can't Go Wrong Plus Free Next Day Shipping
review_body:
Amazon gift cards are nothing new, and they are very handy to give as gifts due to the diverse nature of products Amazon offers – certainly your recipient can find something he / she will like to order.

These gift cards, however, are a little more classy than the standard email or printed-off versions at home as it shows you went a little further, the card is in sturdy packaging, and I appreciate the fact Amazon delivers it for free with next day shipping. If you’re going to be spending $10 or more for a gift card, and have more than one person to give a gift card to, I would recommend you purchase this set of three to your recipients. On the other hand, if you are going to be spending $50 or more on an individual gift card, you may want to consider the gift box option.

review_headline: Can't Go Wrong Plus Free Next Day Shipping
review_body:
Amazon gift cards are nothing new, and they are very handy to give as gifts due to the diverse nature of products Amazon offers – certainly your recipient can find something he / she will like to order.

These gift cards, however, are a little more classy than the standard email or printed-off versions at home as it shows you went a little further, the card is in sturdy packaging, and I appreciate the fact Amazon delivers it for free with next day shipping. If you’re going to be spending $10 or more for a gift card, and have more than one person to give a gift card to, I would recommend you purchase this set of three to your recipients. On the other hand, if you are going to be spending $50 or more on an individual gift card, you may want to consider the gift box option.

product_title: Amazon.com Gift Cards, Pack of 3 (Various Designs)
review_headline: Can't Go Wrong Plus Free Next Day Shipping
review_body:
Amazon gift cards are nothing new, and they are very handy to give as gifts due to the diverse nature of products Amazon offers – certainly your recipient can find something he / she will like to order.

These gift cards, however, are a little more classy than the standard email or printed-off versions at home as it shows you went a little further, the card is in sturdy packaging, and I appreciate the fact Amazon delivers it for free with next day shipping. If you’re going to be spending $10 or more for a gift card, and have more than one person to give a gift card to, I would recommend you purchase this set of three to your recipients. On the other hand, if you are going to be spending $50 or more on an individual gift card, you may want to consider the gift box option.

review_headline: Can't Go Wrong Plus Free Next Day Shipping
review_body:
Amazon gift cards are nothing new, and they are very handy to give as gifts due to the diverse nature of products Amazon offers – certainly your recipient can find something he / she will like to order.

These gift cards, however, are a little more classy than the standard email or printed-off versions at home as it shows you went a little further, the card is in sturdy packaging, and I appreciate the fact Amazon delivers it for free with next day shipping. If you’re going to be spending $10 or more for a gift card, and have more than one person to give a gift card to, I would recommend you purchase this set of three to your recipients. On the other hand, if you are going to be spending $50 or more on an individual gift card, you may want to consider the gift box option.

review_body:
Amazon gift cards are nothing new, and they are very handy to give as gifts due to the diverse nature of products Amazon offers – certainly your recipient can find something he / she will like to order.

These gift cards, however, are a little more classy than the standard email or printed-off versions at home as it shows you went a little further, the card is in sturdy packaging, and I appreciate the fact Amazon delivers it for free with next day shipping. If you’re going to be spending $10 or more for a gift card, and have more than one person to give a gift card to, I would recommend you purchase this set of three to your recipients. On the other hand, if you are going to be spending $50 or more on an individual gift card, you may want to consider the gift box option.

product_title: Amazon.com Gift Cards, Pack of 3 (Various Designs)
review_headline: Can't Go Wrong Plus Free Next Day Shipping
review_body:
Amazon gift cards are nothing new, and they are very handy to give as gifts due to the diverse nature of products Amazon offers – certainly your recipient can find something he / she will like to order.

These gift cards, however, are a little more classy than the standard email or printed-off versions at home as it shows you went a little further, the card is in sturdy packaging, and I appreciate the fact Amazon delivers it for free with next day shipping. If you’re going to be spending $10 or more for a gift card, and have more than one person to give a gift card to, I would recommend you purchase this set of three to your recipients. On the other hand, if you are going to be spending $50 or more on an individual gift card, you may want to consider the gift box option.
